reviewText: Celtic Thunder does nothing wrong bad or other wise.  I lie the old country music of Ireland Scottland the most.  The only thing that is wrong with todays music  that can not ever be changed  is that GEORGE is  now in heaven.  Love the group keep it with the originals , maybe do the spouses and children sing?  Keith / Neil  ???  WHAT'S NOT TO LOVE
Celtic Thunder is a fantastic group!
I loved this DVD.  There is nothing not to love about the celtic Thunder music old or new.  It has always been wonderful.  I have given their music to friends and they love it too.
You can't go wrong with Celtic Thunder!  Came faster than I expected!
I love Celtic Thunder!!!  Everything they do is great and I am sure you will enjoy it too.

Very disappointed as this was not the complete show I saw on TV.  So many parts were cut out.  It should have been noted on the package.  Don't know if I will ever spend my money on a Dvd, I sure felt cheated.
They are fabulous!  Love the dynamics in the group.  The songs and harmony are incredible.
Wonderful talented men with Beautiful voices, Very entertaining!!!
They are a great group. I love their music.
